org.janelia.flyem.neuprint.model

Class Synapse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.janelia.flyem.neuprint.model.Synapse

  • public class Synapse
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a synaptic density. A Synapse has a type (pre or post), a three- dimensional location, a confidence, and a set of rois.
